What are you doing here?

258
00:35:40,416 --> 00:35:42,376
I knew you'd come.

259
00:35:44,879 --> 00:35:47,840
Lucien found it hard to get tickets.

260
00:35:53,304 --> 00:35:55,055
I've a gift for you.

261
00:35:58,225 --> 00:36:02,479
You don't look too well. You could
do with some sun. You're pale.

262
00:36:11,822 --> 00:36:13,115
Ginou!

263
00:36:14,783 --> 00:36:16,827
I'm looking for that watch!

264
00:36:23,459 --> 00:36:26,795
Wat nou? I'm looking for that watch!

265
00:36:27,004 --> 00:36:31,216
In the red Cartier box.
Shit, it was right here!

266
00:36:40,601 --> 00:36:41,852
What's the matter with you?

267
00:36:42,060 --> 00:36:46,023
I'm looking for Marcel's
watch! Where is that watch?

268
00:36:50,986 --> 00:36:55,198
I'm looking for Marcel's watch! What?

269
00:36:56,867 --> 00:37:00,454
Louis? What's the matter?

270
00:37:02,789 --> 00:37:05,000
I want you to be brave, Edith.

271
00:37:07,002 --> 00:37:08,545
Is it Marcel?

272
00:37:10,088 --> 00:37:11,465
What?

273
00:37:14,342 --> 00:37:16,344
The plane crashed...

274
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:36,573
Marcel!

275
00:37:39,659 --> 00:37:41,327
Marcel!

276
00:39:17,214 --> 00:39:19,633
What more can I tell you?

277
00:39:20,718 --> 00:39:22,511
They say you're the best clairvoyant there is.

278
00:39:22,720 --> 00:39:27,725
This is your third visit this
week. I've told you all I know.

279
00:39:28,100 --> 00:39:29,935
Why do you keep coming back?

280
00:39:31,729 --> 00:39:34,314
So you can tell me again.

281
00:39:35,774 --> 00:39:38,902
So that I know why I should continue living.

282
00:39:40,446 --> 00:39:43,574
He died in the air, so
that is where he must be...

283
00:39:55,794 --> 00:39:58,380
<i>California, August 1955</i>

284
00:40:06,805 --> 00:40:12,018
Jack Peals! Can we go any faster? I need air.

285
00:40:12,227 --> 00:40:14,813
I love the heat. It makes me dizzy.

286
00:40:15,730 --> 00:40:18,358
- Step on it. Our pin
- up is melting!

287
