drive. Then Ginou can throw up.

293
00:40:54,144 --> 00:40:55,103
Go on, Ginou.

294
00:40:56,604 --> 00:40:58,189
May I, Madame?

295
00:41:00,400 --> 00:41:01,985
Go ahead, Ginou!

296
00:41:02,652 --> 00:41:04,904
Very good!

297
00:41:10,952 --> 00:41:12,078
Bye bye, Ginou!

298
00:41:12,996 --> 00:41:14,747
Wait for me!

299
00:41:18,751 --> 00:41:20,294
My, you're some driver.

300
00:41:23,464 --> 00:41:28,511
Our journey hasn't been wasted
after all. We just murdered a tree.

301
00:41:36,853 --> 00:41:41,566
My God, the service here is
awful. Can nobody take our order?

302
00:41:42,775 --> 00:41:47,738
<i>Take it easy. You're no star
here. Mocambo is tonight.</i>

303
00:41:47,947 --> 00:41:51,867
